params.lowerRangePercent_: The new lower range to be set
params.upperRangePercent_: The new upper range to be set

setRangesByPercentage(address,int256,int.details: This function can only be called by team multisig

params.newLowerRangePercentage_: The new lower range percentage change, 10000 = 1%. Positive to increase, negative to decrease
params.newUpperRangePercentage_: The new upper range percentage change, 10000 = 1%. Positive to increase, negative to decrease
